It was a gesture of
contempt, a howl of rage,

01:11:30.890 --> 01:11:34.050
the end result of decades of
selfish and unwise decisions

01:11:34.050 --> 01:11:36.570
made by selfish and unwise leaders.

01:11:36.570 --> 01:11:40.340
Happy countries don't elect
Donald Trump president.

01:11:40.340 --> 01:11:42.530
Desperate ones do.

01:11:42.530 --> 01:11:44.810
In retrospect, the lesson seems obvious.

01:11:44.810 --> 01:11:48.630
Ignore voters for long enough
